    "Subsequently training different models on the training set, the performance of each model is evaluated on the testing set to determine which model performs the best.",
    "The model with the highest accuracy is selected and used for future predictions of charging behavior.",
    "The overall charging activity dataset contains data on the charging activity of users at charging stations, including user id, station id, station type, start date, stop date, total duration, and energy usage in watt-hours (wh).",
    "The charging activity dataset is further broken down by vehicle type, including AC usage, DC usage, twowheelers, three-wheelers, and four-wheelers.",
    "Each dataset has the same attributes as the overall charging activity dataset."
